  N4 --> N5[UI: UI Screen (dashboard) + Process Builder (Notification) - Surface updated plan and KPIs to planners; notify stakeholders]
  N5 --> N6[PB: Subject Areas + Report Data - Review outcomes and capture exceptions for learning]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Capacity plan aligned to demand across SKUs/locations with reduced stockouts and waste, improved fill rate and on-time service, and controlled incremental COGS from chosen capacity actions.]
  N3 -->|Projected utilization within toleranc...| B1[Maintain current capacity; trigger rebalancing only for localized imbalances; no ERP writeback needed]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Minimal incremental cost, plan remains stable, monitor for changes]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Minor capacity deficit (can be resolv...| B2[Generate rebalancing actions and automated Kinaxis RapidResponse adjustments; notify planners for confirmation if required]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Service levels protected with low incremental COGS; changes enacted via Kinaxis without major CAPEX]
  O2 --> End[End]
